1. Define a store item as a group
	a. Data definition (10 min)
		A store-item is a
		- book
		- cd
		- dvd
	
	b. Structure definition (5 min)
	c. write template for operations on this structure (5 min) (INDEX CARD)
	d. define two functions that operate on this structure (20 min)
		- get-price : store-item -> number
		- discount : store-item -> store-item
	
2. quiz (10 min)
	a. go over grading guidelines
	b. distribute quiz

3. testing discipline (20 min)
	a. why is testing important?
	b. what are the correct format for tests?
	c. what does test coverage mean?
	d. practice
		- modify tests for previous functions to use correct syntax
		- ensure 100% test coverage
		
4. stepper (remainder)
	a. develop the function find (list->num)
	b. run stepper on function
